       Hell Beast emerged, followed by Marine, Inferno, and Rampage. The 
others were en route to the new base where Shockwave was going to set them 
up. In the meantime, The brotherhood was attacking the Cybertronian Fire and 
Hell Beast was prepared to help.
       "Predacons attack!" He yelled the battle cry and the foursome burst 
into action. The CF was going to be under heavy fire very soon.
